{"type": "article", "id": 30752, "title": "灵感来源于羽翼的柜子", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-08T23:00:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160808213332KEDJ7X05CwhRdoSj.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>Jumphol Socharoentham 和 Pakawat Vijaykadga 都是在泰国先皇理工学院（KMITL）主修家具设计的学生，他们以羽翼为灵感设计了这个名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41332845/ALATO-CABINET\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">ALATO</a> 的柜子。柜子由四根黑色金属管支撑，两扇木门上的木管穿插在表面被喷洒上渐变色的“羽毛”间，从两边打开的样子就像是鸟儿展开翅膀一样，富有新意。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808213935ZqtE8Hkx7hTAM4CR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016080821393745WjGTVzFK1x6iXC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808213937kmF1MJIEKAoBvy9i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808213937kIczsB39Q2TLj1DC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}